        <title>Advanced Loops</title>
        <introduction>A <c>while</c> loop is versitile and all you need to write any Java program. However, there are often multiple statements involved with managing a while loop that could be easier to maintain with more complex but powerful syntax. This section introduces a few new types of loops that provide special-purpose loops to help make your code more manageable.</introduction>
        
